Forts.: 10 July 68
First of all do you eat fruit? You should buy every day one or two schopen
rothde trÑuble, eat them the morning and evening, the morning instead of
caffee or one hour before your caffee, and before your going to bed,

Had you again cramps that you went in the sickroom? I have the omeopathy
pills Frederic has sent them from Stutgart, as soon as you come we shall
try them!

Next sunday papa is to help here in giving the Lord super and preach after-
noon.

What are your brothers writing to you?

I trust the Lord gives you joy.

                              Adieu dear Son
